### 관리자 배너 API 테스트

### 변수
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 관리자 로그인 (토큰 획득)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@admin.com",
  "password": "admin12!!@"
}

> {% client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.data.token) %}

### 배너 생성 또는 업데이트
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "bannerImageUrl": "https://example.com/banner.jpg",
  "clickUrl": "https://example.com/landing",
  "displaySequence": 1
}

### 기존 배너 업데이트
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "bannerImageUrl": "https://example.com/updated-banner.jpg",
  "clickUrl": "https://example.com/updated-landing",
  "displaySequence": 2
}

### ID로 배너 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 모든 배너 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 배너 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/banners/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
